description.plain:
Kid Francescoli is the pop-electro musical project created in 2002 in Marseille by Mathieu Hocine. He has been working for several years with Julia Minkin with whom he co-writes the songs and with Mathieu Chrétien on drums for the concerts.

Kid Francescoli knows success from 2013 on the occasion of the release of his third album, With Julia , marked in particular by the title Blow up and his clip, a short film. The fourth and last album released in 2017, “Play me again” , confirms this success through a new European tour. Finally, the music of Kid Francescoli has been used for commercials of major brands ( Façonnable , Lanvin , Lacoste, Chanel , Lancôme …).

Kid Francescoli is the pop-electro musical project created in 2002 in Marseille by Mathieu Hocine. He has been working for several years with Julia Minkin with whom he co-writes the songs and with Mathieu Chrétien on drums for the concerts.

Kid Francescoli knows success from 2013 on the occasion of the release of his third album, With Julia , marked in particular by the title Blow up and his clip, a short film. The fourth and last album released in 2017, “Play me again” , confirms this success through a new European tour. Finally, the music of Kid Francescoli has been used for commercials of major brands ( Façonnable , Lanvin , Lacoste, Chanel , Lancôme …).
